dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nahiyatay al-Kifl wa Nahr ash-Shah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat Amur al-Misaha. Iraq. Directorate of Surveying Affairs. [[Map of Iraq]: al-Kifl and Nahr ash-Shah sections.] Alternate title: Liwa' al-Hillah: qada' al-Hindiyah: nahiyatah al-Kifl wa Nahr ash-Shah. [Al-Hillah province: al-Hindiyah district: al-Kifl and Nahr ash-Shah sections.] Relief shown by hachures, form lines, and contour lines at random intervals. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1928-29-31. Tribal lands and ownership are shown.
